					"documentation": "# Create Sale Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *RegisteredRegistered* inserts the **title**, **description**, **status** and **price**.\n2. *Registered* selects **publication date**.\n3. *Registered* chooses a **file**.\n4. *System* creates a **Sale** with inserted  data and assigns the **Sale** to the *Registered*.\n\n\n## Alternative flow (Sale is not created)\n\n1. Some fields are **empty**. System informs the *Registered*.\n2. **price** is not a number. System informs the *Registered*.\n3. **publication date** is before today. System informs the *Registered*.\n4. the **Sale** already exist for this *Seller* (same **title**). System informs the *Registered*.\n\n",
					"attributes": [
						{
