					"documentation": "# Look Sales Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *user* inserts a **text**.\n2. *System* displays the active *Sales*(**text**, **description**, **publicationDate**) that contains a **text** in a title.  \n3. If the *Seller** wants to see the details a of a *Sale* extends **Show Sale**.\n\n\n## Alternative flow\n\n1. There are no active **Sales** with a **text** in a **title**, the message describing no sales situation is displayed.\n",
