					"documentation": "# Add to Favorites Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *Registered* inserts a **text**.\n2. System displays the active *Sales*(**text**, **description**, **publicationDate**) that contains a **text** in a title. \n3. *Registered* insert a sell **key**.\n4. System displays the information associated to a **Sale** with this saleNumber **key** (**title**, **description**, **status**, **price**, **publicationDate and file**).\n5. *Registered* select a **Sale**.\n6. *Registered* push the **Favorites** button.\n7. System add the **sale** to favorite list.\n\n\n## Alternative flow\n\n1. There are no active **Sales** with a **text** in a **title**, the message describing no sales situation is displayed.\n2. If there is any attribute with no value, the field will be empty.",
