					"documentation": "# Make an Offer Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *Registered* press the **offer buton** on the sale\n2. *Registered* writes the amount that will pay\n3. *system* sends the offer\n\n\n## Alternative flow\n\n1. *Registered* writes a invalid amount\n2. *systm* display error mesage\n",
