					"documentation": "# Deposit Money Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *Registered* press the **profile button**\n2. *Registered* writes the amount in the amount gap.\n3. *Registered* press the **Withdraw money button**\n\n\n## Alternative flow\n\n1. The *amount* is empty / not numeric / <= 0 System displays a error message.",
